    {
      "id": "8485",
      "label": "1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Do the following:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8493",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Choose an item that your family might want to purchase that is considered a major expense."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8486",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Write a plan that tells how your family would save money for the purchase identified in requirement 1(a)."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8487",
          "label": "1",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Discuss the plan with your counselor."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8488",
          "label": "2",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Discuss the plan with your family."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8489",
          "label": "3",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Discuss how other family needs must be considered in this plan."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8490",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Develop a written shopping strategy for the purchase identified in requirement 1(a)."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8491",
          "label": "1",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Determine the quality of the item or service (using consumer publications or rating systems.)"
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8492",
          "label": "2",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Comparison shop for the item. Find out where you can buy the item for the best price. (Provide prices from at least two different price sources.) Call around; study ads. Look for a sale or discount coupon. Consider alternatives. Can you buy the item used? Should you wait for a sale?"
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8494",
      "label": "2",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Do the following:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8498",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Prepare a budget reflecting your expected income (allowance, gifts, wages), expenses, and savings for a period of 13 consecutive weeks."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8495",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Compare expected income with expected expenses."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8496",
          "label": "1",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "If expenses exceed budget income, determine steps to balance your budget."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8497",
          "label": "2",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "If income exceeds budget expenses, state how you would use the excess money (new goal, savings)."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8777",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Track and record your actual income, expenses, and savings for 13 consecutive weeks (the same 13-week period for which you budgeted). (You may use the forms provided in the "
            },
            {
              "type": "element",
              "tag": "em",
              "attrs": {},
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "Personal Management"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " merit badge pamphlet, devise your own, or use a computer-generated version). When complete, present the records showing the results to your counselor."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8778",
          "label": "d",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Compare your budget with your actual income and expenses to understand when your budget worked and when it did not work. With your counselor, discuss what you might do differently the next time."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8499",
      "label": "3",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Discuss with your counselor FIVE of the following concepts:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8500",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The emotions you feel when you receive money."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8501",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Your understanding of how the amount of money you have with you affects your spending habits."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8502",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Your thoughts when you buy something new and your thoughts about the same item three months later. Explain the concept of buyer's remorse."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8503",
          "label": "d",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "How hunger affects you when shopping for food items (snacks, groceries)."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8504",
          "label": "e",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Your experience of an item you have purchased after seeing or hearing advertisements for it. Did the item work as well as advertised?"
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8505",
          "label": "f",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Your understanding of what happens when you put money into a savings account."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8506",
          "label": "g",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Charitable giving. Explain its purpose and your thoughts about it."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8507",
          "label": "h",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "What you can do to better manage your money."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8508",
      "label": "4",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Explain the following to your counselor:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8509",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The differences between saving and investing, including reasons for using one over the other."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8510",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The concepts of return on investment and risk and how they are related."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8511",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The concepts of simple interest and compound interest."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8545",
          "label": "d",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The concept of diversification in investing."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8546",
          "label": "e",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Why it is important to save and invest for retirement."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
